      "span_text": "The cytotoxic activity of the synthesized complexes against the HeLa, C6, and CHO cell lines was determined using the colorimetric 3-(4,5-dimethylthiazol-2-yl)-2,5-diphenyl tetrazolium bromide (MTT) assay. This assay was carried out in triplicate in 96 well plates [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] ."
